This?

705
00:42:59,182 --> 00:43:00,645
Wouldn't it be better to kill someone like that?

706
00:43:00,670 --> 00:43:01,184
Idiot!

707
00:43:01,561 --> 00:43:04,996
I don't use my pistol for murderer... Oh... I slipped up there

708
