Sorry for keeping you waiting.

781
00:48:09,395 --> 00:48:12,036
Oh? Dad! Dad!

782
00:48:12,481 --> 00:48:13,895
What are you doing?

783
00:48:14,640 --> 00:48:15,826
She's calling Dad!

784
00:48:15,973 --> 00:48:17,456
Did she keep her father waiting?

785
00:48:17,480 --> 00:48:18,296
You're such a fool

786
