Who would wait for their real father
while taking a bath?

787
00:48:21,371 --> 00:48:22,052
What do you mean?

788
00:48:22,207 --> 00:48:26,270
That man gives her a lot of money.

789
00:48:26,434 --> 00:48:27,380
