Wait! Boss, Forgive me....

801
00:49:29,710 --> 00:49:34,128
I really have to team up with you after all

802
00:49:34,680 --> 00:49:38,206
Please let the past be the past, I beg you

803
00:49:38,300 --> 00:49:39,183
Boss

804
